Jacinta Stapleton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jacinta_Stapleton 0 Jacinta Patrice Stapleton (born 6 June 1979) is an Australian actress. Her most notable acting role was Amy Greenwood in the Australian television soap opera Neighbours from 1997 to 2000. She is the younger sister of Blindspot actor Sullivan Stapleton.
